prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D illustration for a greeting card. In a dreamy fantasy art style, an illustrated version of Jordan from the photo is playfully piggybacking an illustrated version of Lao Lao from the photo. They both have joyful, energetic expressions and are laughing. Jordan wears a maroon t-shirt and Lao Lao wears the yellow floral dress from the photo. They are running through a magical, oversized forest at twilight where the flora glows with soft neon light. Fantastical, whimsical creatures like tiny winged foxes and glowing sprites peek out from behind giant, iridescent mushrooms and luminous, swirling ferns. The air is filled with floating, sparkling dust motes and gentle bubbles of light. In the center of the image, the text "Happy Birthday, my love" is written in a beautiful, readable, glowing white handwritten cursive script. The overall composition is dynamic and full of movement, with a vibrant, ethereal color palette of deep blues, purples, pinks, and glowing teals.
